modShortDescription: This 7 Days to Die mod increases the amount of zombies in the world and also forces night zombies spawns to every night instead of vanillas every 3 nights.
modDescription:
This 7 Days to Die mod increases the amount of [zombies](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-zombies/) in the world and also forces night zombies spawns to every night instead of vanillas every 3 nights. How crazy are you? It’s up to you.
